shortDescription.default: This web part fetches all the automatically added Header anchor tags in a SharePoint page and displays them in a Navigation component. When added to a Vertical Section, it can be used as a table of contents for the page.

longDescription.default: This web part fetches all the automatically added Header anchor tags in a SharePoint page and displays them in a Navigation component. When added to a Vertical Section, it can be used as a table of contents for the page.
